  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is conducted in Asia. The aim of this observational study is to evaluate the side
      effects profile and benefits of using intravenous insulin aspart infusion in hospitalised
      subjects under normal clinical practice conditions in India.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
